Test.Cardano.Ledger.Constrained.Conway.Instances

Contents

  • Orphan instances

Description

This module provides the necessary instances of HasSpec and HasSimpleRep to write specs for the environments, states, and signals in the conway STS rules. Note some simple types used in the PParams (Coin, EpochInterval, etc.) have their instances defined in Test.Cardano.Ledger.Constrained.Conway.InstancesBasic and they are reexported here.
